BEGIN:VCALENDAR
VERSION:2.0
PRODID:-//USMC Chaplain Command//365 Unified Holidays//EN
CALSCALE:GREGORIAN
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260201
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260330
SUMMARY:Phase I: Festival of Purification, Fasting, and First Light
DESCRIPTION:USO Sponsored. Spanning Imbolc, Lupercalia, Ramadan, Eid al-Fitr, Purim, Tlacaxipehualiztli, and Ostara. Focus on fasting, purification, and deliverance. Attach Accommodation Requests for fasting Marines.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260402
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260530
SUMMARY:Phase II: Festival of Liberation, Growth, and Sacrifice
DESCRIPTION:USO Sponsored. Spanning Passover, Megalesia, Cerealia, Beltane, Toxcatl, Shavuot, and Eid al-Adha. Focus on liberation, the law, and sacrifice. USO BBQs and feasts. Attach Facility Requests.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260616
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260802
SUMMARY:Phase III: Festival of Solstice, Ancestors, and Remembrance
DESCRIPTION:USO Sponsored. Spanning Islamic New Year, Ashura, Litha, Huey Tecuilhuitl, Neptunalia, Tisha B'Av, Wepet Renpet, and Lughnasadh. Focus on honoring the fallen, hydration, and solstice. Attach Ceremony Supplements.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260911
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261104
SUMMARY:Phase IV: Festival of Harvest, Atonement, and the Hunt
DESCRIPTION:USO Sponsored. Spanning High Holy Days (Rosh Hashanah/Yom Kippur/Sukkot), Mawlid an-Nabi, Mabon, Quecholli, and Samhain. Focus on atonement, harvest, and hunting/warfare prep. Attach Accommodation Requests.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261204
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270101
SUMMARY:Phase V: Festival of Light, Dedication, and the Year's End
DESCRIPTION:USO Sponsored. Spanning Hanukkah, Saturnalia, Yule, and the 5 Epagomenal/Nemontemi days. Focus on light, gifts, and rank-inversion dinners. USO Care Packages distributed. Attach Facility Requests.
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR